Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:07.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（危險）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:08.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（不要犯困）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:09.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（不—要—犯—困）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀—！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.89,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,…事件發生的時間是昨天下午三點多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經早上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做了個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼是那種夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,租金3萬日圓以內  距離車站步行1分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電視一直開著的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚會下雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這個時候了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我到底在幹甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要到甚麼時候才能變成蝴蝶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡懶覺也得有個分寸喲  青蟲君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「7月14日  冰涼和鬱馥」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天小宮沒來叫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不會是小宮也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考試遲到就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然小宮也學習到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學習？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是單純的睡過頭了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都睡了十二個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十二個小時…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來總算能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時候就會覺得住在學校門前真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？香草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,豎琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：由乃把herb誤聽作harp了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始學豎琴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不貴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是最後一天考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶齊文具了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才急急忙忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可塑橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  你帶了兩塊橡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個這麼著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一個得這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡要如此做…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶…偶然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個這麼著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個選這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後下一個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得一定是弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家開始動筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師的美術課考試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這照片上的人物是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}美術\N問一\N這照片上的人物是誰呢？\N請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼美術考試會有日本史的題目…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}問二\N這照片上的人物是誰呢？\N請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,織田信長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}問三\N這照片上的人物是誰呢？\N請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本…本名叫甚麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摩艾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請舉出你喜歡的一位藝術家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就不是考試而是調查問卷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請舉出一幅你喜歡的繪畫作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}問十二\N請舉出一幅你喜歡的繪畫作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繪畫…繪畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請舉出一件你喜歡的雕塑作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雕塑…雕塑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,列舉三個以上  你最喜歡的吉野屋老師的動人之處告訴校長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分值…五十分？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,濫用職權
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（我肚子餓了）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想在試卷上塗鴉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很明顯和在寫字時不一樣的聲音不絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:42.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（手癢癢）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手癢癢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手癢癢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手癢癢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:07:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣期末考試就全部結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一排的同學請把試卷收上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分數最低的同學的答題卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要張貼到校門口去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做好心理準備喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於被校長狠狠地訓了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不張貼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想到考試結束了就是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就太過興奮而不能集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,湛藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耀眼的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO  GO  黑色素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  日光浴喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是來曬太陽的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起曬黑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮莫非你剛在房頂上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能做那麼危險的事情喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摔下來就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做日光浴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然夏天就得是健康的黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腹部都弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腹部好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真是熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說因為在夏天這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就這樣也很可以享受一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有甚麼變涼快的方法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼故事  鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,臺階？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:21.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnzhunyuan\b1}（注：「怪談」、「階段」兩個詞發音一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說爬到最上面會很涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是中途就會舉手投降了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是鬼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  臺階
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是鬼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是臺階
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是臺階
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是外星人～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地底人～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:10:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無農葯栽培的胡蘿蔔～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的  沙英學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也經常這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們做…做…做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也不敲門就闖入別人屋裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是個大太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們想或許一樓比二樓涼快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  考試也全考完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沙英學姐也和我們一塊兒玩的話會很開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  尋似乎很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還說要在屋裡製作作品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天也沒有甚麼特別的要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做甚麼？翻翻看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有甚麼有意思的東西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  甚麼甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「我最喜歡和美了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俊君突然站了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對著逐漸沉下水平線的太陽大喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已超過預定時間五個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在淅瀝的雨中連傘也沒撐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優作只是一個勁地在等著恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼優作是那麼的溫柔呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  沙英學姐真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不是更熱了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去泳池嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你邀別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？為甚麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那說來很難為情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是個鋸子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（由乃想說的是這個…金づち(旱鴨子)）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說錯得很離譜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我明白那玩意同樣會在水裡沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿泳池來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿泳池來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,橡膠泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…也罷  雖說我就想會是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼你有這玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,決定一個人住的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父母讓我帶上這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯的父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個在一個人住的時候有必要嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說即使租沒有浴室的房間也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼父母啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過   這個泳池的話由乃也no problem了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  或許用這個我也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說甚麼沒有問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這泳池裡你想溺水也沒法子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來宮子  你有泳衣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有學校發的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣不就覺得像是在學校游泳一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件去年買的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子  這個你拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,T-shirt和比基尼短褲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？沙英學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼比基尼沒有上下配套呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是弄丟了上裝甚麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是不想被宮子說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼「胸部好緊啊」之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙…沙英學姐很苗條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或…或許是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對喲  沙英學姐這裡有個院子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是住一樓的人的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  由乃來吹氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚前能吹起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄錯了弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非由乃沒用過氣泵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  過去也玩過橡膠泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那時候我還小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是爸爸幫我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說來這玩意平時不大用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用的時候就是讓橡膠泳池啊橡膠艇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種的氣墊膨脹起來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泳圈啊沙灘排球啊甚麼的用嘴吹還方便些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣  氣泵可是我的絕活喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都差不多想在簡歷裡的特長一欄寫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（使用氣泵三級）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  去換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子  泳池就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,氣泵把…空氣…送進去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送空氣…很費勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在做甚麼啊  尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自我忍耐比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在進行製作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我在製作能穿著夏天的短裝的苗條身材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這種製作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英你們這樣子是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在戲水的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮拿來了橡膠泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本想也邀尋學姐一起來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然說到夏天就應該是火鍋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可沒有聽說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來  這麼熱你還吃得下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  偶爾也會想吃火鍋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以攝取許多蔬菜  對健康有好處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡甚麼火鍋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡鹹雜燴火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是日式牛肉火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什錦火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是泡菜火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為能減肥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  火鍋就得大家一起吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  別在那兒光吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  火鍋奉行出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（火鍋奉行：吃火鍋時樂於規定他人食材何時放入，何時能吃的人）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼火鍋會有奉行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發號施令這種了不起的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了奉行也還有很多其他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會說是火鍋社長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了別光吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋社長是火鍋職員的社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋同心甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：江戶時代類似警察一類的下級官差）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋老中甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.61,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：江戶幕府時期最高的官職）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋總統甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋總理大臣甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我～說～了～別光吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋預告師甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋領頭美容師甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火鍋Best Genius甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到底在做甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想想今天真的好熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一般的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是更加健康的減肥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰涼冰涼的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,現在插播特別新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天以來一直持續著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣只看著天空的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會感覺像在海裡悠閒地漂著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  會哦會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是白令海了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼是白令海？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加勒比海甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愛琴海甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更加休閒的大海也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一陣子沒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起大海我還是喜歡泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為腳不能著地是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是鋸子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鋸子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  鋸啊鋸啊鋸啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過為甚麼海邊的店裡的的拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會有特別好的味道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咖喱飯也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  食物已經說夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說完全跑題了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天做了個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被斗篷一樣的紅色的布團追著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夢是表現人的深層心理的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說由乃不想被紅色的斗篷追著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你照搬嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說或許那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是卷積雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每年看著那雲都會想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  暑假你準備怎麼過？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是去大海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  我可是鋸子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說那個鋸子是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鋸子  鋸子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接近傍晚的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（夏天的海）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼樣對付過了考試
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也沒有像是要開紅燈的科目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個莫非是紅色的窗簾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的窗簾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,略作「紅燈」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：文字遊戲）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷笑話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青蟲君它…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青蟲君它…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蛾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青蟲君原來是蛾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點奇形怪狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要上這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  從窗子飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到尋學姐屋裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,7月14日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小時侯做過晴天娃娃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  做過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,郊遊甚麼的運動會甚麼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為  面對自然現象做這種事情也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比平時起得更早  背上背包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交換盒飯裡的小菜甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:23:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  覺得有些興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  Stop！之後的且聽下回分解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次是「10月12日  暴風雨的乾燥劑」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在暖陽莊等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要來看哦
